<content>
    <chapter line="1">Dhammacakkapavattanadīpanīgāthā</chapter>
    <hangnum line="2" number="174"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="3"> Sammāsambodhiñānaṃ hatasakalamalaṃ suddhato cātisuddhaṃ,</gatha1>
    <gatha2 line="4">Addhā laddhā suladdhaṃ vatamiti satataṃ cintayanto subodhiṃ;</gatha2>
    <gatha3 line="5">Sattāhaṃ sattamevaṃ vividhaphalasukhaṃ vitināmesi kālaṃ,</gatha3>
    <gathalast line="6">Brahmenāyācito so isipatanavane vattayī dhammacakkaṃ.</gathalast>
